divs: sighting detailsthe large circular object on the far left could be a mother ship. notice the bulge and possible opening on the bottom side of it. the other object is much smaller and white. there were several of the smaller type objects in the sky but not close enough to be in the picture. i took the photo from my front yard on sunday 7\2\06 about 12:45 in the afternoon. i enclosed a picture of the original and an enlargement of each of the other two objects.
Summary: Possible mother ship and small ship
